  "description": "You must tell DVLA if you have pulmonary arterial hypertension and you're receiving treatment from a specialist centre - download the correct form to let them know.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You must tell DVLA if you have pulmonary arterial hypertension and you’re <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/pulmonary-hypertension/treatment/\">receiving treatment from an NHS specialist centre</a>.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Warning\" class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you do not tell DVLA about a condition that affects your driving. You may be prosecuted if you’re involved in an accident as a result.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"car-or-motorcycle-licence\">Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/government/publications/report-your-medical-condition-form-ph1\">Fill in form PAH1</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"bus-coach-or-lorry-licence\">Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/government/publications/report-your-medical-condition-form-ph1v\">Fill in form PAH1V</a> and send it to DVLA. The address is on the form.</p>\n",
